title: The Punch Song Lyrics Aaha Kalyanam Song Lyrics
stanzas:
Song: The Punch Song
Lyrics: Karky
Singers: M.M.Manasi, Nivas
Movie: Aaha Kalyanam
Music: Dharan Kumar

Naan thala da, nanbenda
naan thani aalu,
all is well.
Malada annamalada
kooti kalichi paaru kanakku sariyavarum

Ongi naan adicha ondra ton weightu da
nee adichaa peesu naan adichaa maasu
adambula kai irukkum kaalirukkum
mookkirukkum muliyirukkum
aana uyir irukkaadhu.

Vada en machi valakka bajji
naandhaanda gilli adipenda solli
my name is billa suduvenda nalla
chutti the robo muttaadha po po (2)

nakka nakkka nakka nakk..
Venaaam...
naan eppo varuven
eppadi varuven yaarukkum theriyadhu

Sollama varradhu..
sollitu varadhu veerasamy
lateah vandhaalum latesta varuven
ketadhayum tharuven ketkadhayum varuven
mudhala yaaru first varraanganu mukkiyamla
kadasiyila yaaru first varraaganuthan mukkiyam

Vada en machi valakka bajji
naandhaanda gilli adipenda solli
my name is billa suduvenda nalla
chutti the robo muttaadha po po (2) 

En vazhkayila ovvoru nimishamum .
ovvoru nodiyum naan sedhukkunadhu.
naanum konja naala
nalla.. nadikkuradhu

neenga nallavaraa illa kettavaraa.
naan thanimaram illa thoppu.
idhu seththa kootamilla
anbaala serndha koottam.

Vada en machi valakka bajji
naandhaanda gilli adipenda solli
my name is billa suduvenda nalla
chutti the robo muttaadha po po (2)

Naan thala da, nanbenda
naan thani aalu,
all is well.
Malada annamalada.
kooti kalichi paaru kanakku sariyavarum.

Ongi naan adicha ondra ton weightu da.
nee adichaa peesu naan adichaa maasu.
adambula kai irukkum kaalirukkum
mookkirukkum muliyirukkum
aana uyir irukkaadhu.

Kanna panninga koottama varum
singam singlea thaan varum.
